# Web Service Quality Classification

This project predicts the quality of web services based on performance metrics using Machine Learning.

- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Random Forest Algorithm

Contains service metrics like response time, uptime, and latency.

- Data preprocessing
- Label encoding
- Model training using Random Forest
- Quality prediction of services

Predicts whether a service is Good, Average, or Bad.
